  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881810/extras/bafa16d74f3560ccd3d627a9f3f0fe8c.webp?t=1745533510\" width=600 height=38 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Intro</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into Commander Bug Wars and take control in a wild battle between Terrans and Cyber Bugs. This is the ultimate turn-based game where your decisions matter. Get ready for epic fun and see if you can lead your side to victory!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881810/extras/f5346f956b74d4eec1bff29858b7211d.poster.avif?t=1745533510\" width=596 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881810/extras/f5346f956b74d4eec1bff29858b7211d.webm?t=1745533510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881810/extras/f5346f956b74d4eec1bff29858b7211d.mp4?t=1745533510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Description</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump into the action as you fight for supremacy in exciting campaigns and skirmishes. Customize your game and challenge up to seven other commanders. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Two Factions: Choose between Terrans and Bugs in your quest for domination. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Faction unique units: Each faction has unique units and their own set of abilities. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Variety of Units: Use infantry, tanks, planes, and ships to strengthen your forces. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strategic Points: Capture key locations to keep your resources flowing. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Terrain Tactics: Use the landscape to your advantage in every battle. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Special Units: Deploy unique units to counter your enemies. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Map Editor: Create your own battlegrounds and test your strategies. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to become the ultimate commander in Commander Bug Wars? The battlefield is waiting for you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881810/extras/286f425c034ac509c43f8486ec68bddd.poster.avif?t=1745533510\" width=596 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881810/extras/286f425c034ac509c43f8486ec68bddd.webm?t=1745533510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881810/extras/286f425c034ac509c43f8486ec68bddd.mp4?t=1745533510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881810/extras/bafa16d74f3560ccd3d627a9f3f0fe8c.webp?t=1745533510\" width=600 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881810/extras/44d0e6eaf58bf65d1bfaa242197b5800.poster.avif?t=1745533510\" width=596 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881810/extras/44d0e6eaf58bf65d1bfaa242197b5800.webm?t=1745533510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881810/extras/44d0e6eaf58bf65d1bfaa242197b5800.mp4?t=1745533510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881810/extras/bafa16d74f3560ccd3d627a9f3f0fe8c.webp?t=1745533510\" width=600 height=38 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Intro</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into Commander Bug Wars and take control in a wild battle between Terrans and Cyber Bugs. This is the ultimate turn-based game where your decisions matter. Get ready for epic fun and see if you can lead your side to victory!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881810/extras/f5346f956b74d4eec1bff29858b7211d.poster.avif?t=1745533510\" width=596 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881810/extras/f5346f956b74d4eec1bff29858b7211d.webm?t=1745533510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881810/extras/f5346f956b74d4eec1bff29858b7211d.mp4?t=1745533510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Description</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump into the action as you fight for supremacy in exciting campaigns and skirmishes. Customize your game and challenge up to seven other commanders. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Two Factions: Choose between Terrans and Bugs in your quest for domination. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Faction unique units: Each faction has unique units and their own set of abilities. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Variety of Units: Use infantry, tanks, planes, and ships to strengthen your forces. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strategic Points: Capture key locations to keep your resources flowing. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Terrain Tactics: Use the landscape to your advantage in every battle. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Special Units: Deploy unique units to counter your enemies. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Map Editor: Create your own battlegrounds and test your strategies. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to become the ultimate commander in Commander Bug Wars? The battlefield is waiting for you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881810/extras/286f425c034ac509c43f8486ec68bddd.poster.avif?t=1745533510\" width=596 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881810/extras/286f425c034ac509c43f8486ec68bddd.webm?t=1745533510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881810/extras/286f425c034ac509c43f8486ec68bddd.mp4?t=1745533510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881810/extras/bafa16d74f3560ccd3d627a9f3f0fe8c.webp?t=1745533510\" width=600 height=38 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881810/extras/44d0e6eaf58bf65d1bfaa242197b5800.poster.avif?t=1745533510\" width=596 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881810/extras/44d0e6eaf58bf65d1bfaa242197b5800.webm?t=1745533510\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881810/extras/44d0e6eaf58bf65d1bfaa242197b5800.mp4?t=1745533510\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
